schools.name: John Marshall School of Business and Civic Leadership

data.description: Welcome to your charming Cape Cod in Cleveland! This home offers four bedrooms and two full bathrooms, providing space and comfort for your family. The interior boasts both an inviting eat-in kitchen and a separate dining room, perfect for meals and gatherings. The convenience of a first-floor master bedroom, ensuring easy living, while three additional spacious bedrooms await on the upper level. The basement adds additional space for entertainment, featuring a recreation room. Outside, the front of the home boasts a small front porch, ideal for enjoying the Cleveland breeze. You'll appreciate the practicality of a two-car detached garage, while the fenced-in yard offers privacy and security for pets and outdoor activities. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours! The roof has a transferable warranty.
